WEBVTT

00:01:58.502 --> 00:02:01.119
and when we said: "I caught you!"

00:02:02.186 --> 00:02:03.880
he would look around for us,

00:02:04.970 --> 00:02:09.709
and at that moment,
I could feel he was alive.

00:02:13.088 --> 00:02:18.015
We also hold a record for hours spent
in a swimming pool.

00:02:19.182 --> 00:02:22.538
Ivan always had a passion for water.

00:02:23.834 --> 00:02:26.691
I remember when he was two and a half,

00:02:27.761 --> 00:02:31.061
on a rainy winter day,